name: Green Reaper by Matt Furie
description: The Green Reaper first appeared in Matt Furie’s hand-drawn Hedz NFT collection, later shown in art galleries alongside other characters that were later confirmed to be in Cortex Vortex.Now, thanks to a post by Furie’s editor on Instagram , it’s official: Green Reaper is part of the book’s universe.There are whispers he may be the next villain in the Boys Club saga — opposing Pepe, Landwolf, Andy, and Brett.
